variables {R : Type*} [comm_ring R]
variables {a b c d : R}

theorem det_2x2 (A : matrix (fin 2) (fin 2) R) 
  (hA : A = ![![a, b], ![c, d]]) : A.det = a * d - b * c :=
begin
  simp [matrix.det_fin_two, hA],
end

variables {R : Type*} [comm_ring R]
